---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Finance Options | Sunshine Tiny Houses"
  description="Flexible finance options for your tiny house or modular home. Access 50+ lenders through Emu Money, or apply through Handypay for loans up to $75,000."
  canonical="https://www.sunshinetinyhouses.com.au/finance/"
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Finance</p>
      <h1>Finance Options</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">Flexible finance to help make your tiny house or modular home a reality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container finance-intro">
      <p>We've partnered with two trusted finance providers so you can get into your new home sooner. Whether you're looking for a personal loan or want access to a broad range of lenders, we can help point you in the right direction.</p>
      <p>Enquiring doesn't affect your credit score, and you're under no obligation to proceed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="finance-cards">

        <div class="finance-card">
          <div class="finance-card__header">
            <p class="eyebrow">Finance Partner</p>
            <h2>Emu Money</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="finance-card__intro">Access to 50+ Australian lenders through one simple application — personal and business finance options available.</p>
          <ul class="finance-features">
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F4C5;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Loan terms</strong>
                <span>6 to 60 months</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F3E6;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Lender access</strong>
                <span>50+ Australian lenders</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x26A1;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Fast approval</strong>
                <span>Typically 24–48 hours</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F4B3;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Options</strong>
                <span>Personal and business finance</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="finance-steps">
            <h3>How it works</h3>
            <ol>
              <li>Browse our designs and get a quote</li>
              <li>Submit your online application</li>
              <li>Receive fast approval</li>
              <li>Move into your new space</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="finance-card">
          <div class="finance-card__header">
            <p class="eyebrow">Finance Partner</p>
            <h2>Handypay</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="finance-card__intro">A straightforward personal loan with competitive rates — up to $75,000 per applicant, with two joint applicants able to finance up to $150,000.</p>
          <ul class="finance-features">
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F4B0;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Loan range</strong>
                <span>$2,001 – $75,000 per applicant</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F4C5;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Available terms</strong>
                <span>1 to 7 years</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F4C6;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Repayments</strong>
                <span>Weekly, fortnightly or monthly</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon">&#x1F4C8;</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Rate from</strong>
                <span>6.29% p.a. (comparison rate 6.80%)</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="finance-eligibility">
            <h3>Eligibility</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>18+ years old</li>
              <li>Australian citizen or permanent resident</li>
              <li>Must have employment income</li>
              <li>Consumer use only</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="finance-note">Enquiring doesn't impact your credit score. Approved in seconds — Handypay covers the upfront cost and payments align with your income schedule.</p>
          <p class="finance-contact">Call Handypay direct: <a href="tel:1300990115">1300 990 115</a></p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container finance-cta">
      <h2>Ready to Explore Your Options?</h2>
      <p>Get in touch with us first and we can point you to the right finance partner for your project.</p>
      <div class="finance-cta__btns">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:0753158365" class="btn btn--outline">(07) 5315 8365</a>
      </div>
      <p class="finance-disclaimer">Finance is subject to lending criteria and your personal circumstances. Interest rates are indicative and may vary. Always read the product disclosure before applying.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-hero {
  background: var(--color-surface-dark);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
}
.page-hero h1 { color: #fff; }
.page-hero__sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); margin-top: .75rem; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 560px; }

.finance-intro p { color: var(--color-text-body); max-width: 680px; }
.finance-intro p + p { margin-top: .75rem; }

.finance-cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
}

.finance-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
}
.finance-card__header { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.finance-card__header h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
.finance-card__intro { color: var(--color-text-body); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.65; }

.finance-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .85rem; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
.finance-features li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: .85rem; }
.feature-icon { font-size: 1.25rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .1rem; }
.finance-features strong { display: block; font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); }
.finance-features span { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--color-text-body); }

.finance-steps h3,
.finance-eligibility h3 { font-size: .9rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: .6rem; }
.finance-steps ol { padding-left: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; }
.finance-steps ol li { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--color-text-body); line-height: 1.55; }
.finance-eligibility ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .3rem; }
.finance-eligibility ul li { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--color-text-body); }

.finance-note { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--color-text-body); margin-top: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; }
.finance-contact { font-size: .88rem; margin-top: .6rem; font-weight: 600; }
.finance-contact a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

.finance-cta { text-align: center; }
.finance-cta h2 { margin-bottom: .75rem; }
.finance-cta p { color: var(--color-text-body); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
.finance-cta__btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.finance-disclaimer { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--color-text-body); opacity: .7; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto; }

.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: .9rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
  text-align: center;
}
.btn--primary { background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; }
.btn--primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-hover); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.btn--outline { background: transparent; color: var(--color-primary); border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); }
.btn--outline:hover { background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; }

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .finance-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
